    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "2018 sedan in good condition. The engine and transmission are in reliable working order with no known mechanical problems. The exterior shows some minor paint chips and light scratches from regular use. The interior is well-maintained with only slight signs of wear on the upholstery.",
